The street, lined with trees and buildings, stretches out into the distance. The buildings, predominantly white and gray, rise up against the backdrop of a clear blue sky. The trees, lush and green, add a touch of nature to the urban landscape. People can be seen walking on the sidewalks, adding a sense of life and activity to the scene. The image is bathed in the warm glow of the sun, casting long shadows and highlighting the architectural details of the buildings.
